text: Eudryoctenes africanus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Karl Jordan in 1903.BioLib.cz - Eudryoctenes africanus. Retrieved 8 September 2014. ==Subspecies== * Eudryoctenes africanus africanus (Jordan, 1903) * Eudryoctenes africanus orientalis Breuning, 1958 * Eudryoctenes africanus togonicus (Hintz, 1919) ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1903
title: Eudryoctenes africanus
